<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Job Application Stage</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h2 {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        text-align: left;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #666;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 1.2em;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background: #0056b3;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        text-align: left;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Job Application Stage Update</h2>
      <p>Dear <%= candidateName %>,</p>
      <p>
        We wanted to update you on the stage of your application for the
        position of <%= jobTitle %> at <%= companyName %>.
      </p>
      <p>Your current application stage is: <%= stageName %></p>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
      <a href="<%= companyWebsite %>" class="btn">Visit Our Website</a>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Head HR</p>
        <p><%= companyName %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
